Stewart Buys G&T Metallurgical for Undisclosed Sum, FT Reports

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-02-16T05:17:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/stewart-buys-g-t-metallurgical-for-undisclosed-sum-ft-reports.html
Stewart Group Ltd., a privately
owned U.K. metals and minerals inspection company, has bought
G&T Metallurgical Services Ltd. of  Canada  for an undisclosed
sum, the Financial Times reported, citing Stewart Managing
Director John Notman-Watt.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 